flobby is a spring (http://springrts.com) lobby client written in C++.
It is developed and tested on archlinux.

Dependencies worth noting:
FLTK 1.3
boost
C++11 (gcc 4.6 should be ok)
pr-downloader (runtime optional)

To be able to download maps from within flobby you need pr-downloader installed.
Get pr-downloader at https://github.com/abma/pr-downloader. 

Build and run:
cmake .
make flobby
src/flobby

